lyrics:

I don't know what color your eyes are, baby

And you don't come from this town

I'm alive, huh, huh, so alive
I'm alive, huh, huh, so alive

I'm alive, huh, huh, so alive
I'm alive, huh, huh, so alive

I don't know what color your eyes are, baby

[Chorus]
